374
化學應用群論 Group Theory for Chemistry
http://ocw.nctu.edu.tw/course_detail.php?bgid=1&gid=2&nid=374
化學應用群論 Group Theory for Chemistry


課程首頁

本課程是由交通大學應用化學系提供。

Group theory provides a systematic mathematical method for describing molecular symmetry. Actually each kind of symmetry corresponds to one of conservation law that is experimentally observable. Properties of a group, symmetry operations and symmetry elements, molecular symmetry groups, representations and characters all are used to describe molecular orbitals, molecular vibrations, selection rules, and so on.
--
